      • MembersSetProfileArg

        public MembersSetProfileArg(UserSelectorArg user,
                            String newEmail,
                            String newExternalId,
                            String newGivenName,
                            String newSurname)
        Exactly one of team_member_id, email, or external_id must be provided to identify the user account. At least one of new_email, new_external_id, new_given_name, and/or new_surname must be provided.

        Use newBuilder to create instances of this class without specifying values for all optional fields.

        Parameters:
        user - Identity of user whose profile will be set. Must not be null.
        newEmail - New email for member.
        newExternalId - New external ID for member.
        newGivenName - New given name for member.
        newSurname - New surname for member.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If any argument does not meet its preconditions.
